#### Airlock Digital

#### Overview

This dashboard provides a comprehensive view of execution events captured by Airlock Digital across your environment. It helps security teams identify blocked and untrusted activity, analyze execution trends, and drill down into specific process behaviors.

Total, Blocked, and Untrusted Executions provide an overview of event volumes and trust levels; Executions by Type shows categorical distribution. Top Users, Hosts, Files, Parent Processes, and Policies highlight the most frequent entities involved. Executions over Time reveals trends, while Execution History Details offers granular event-level data.
